## Keep the Docker build context lean. Both docker/Dockerfile (release) and
## docker/Dockerfile.dev build with the repo root as context.
## Needed in context: Go sources, go.mod/go.sum, migrations/, templates/,
## static/ (dist is prebuilt by `make assets` in CI), scripts/, package.json.
.git
.github
.claude
node_modules
notes
docs
deploy
tmp
.tmp
docket
.env
*.md
